    "body": "Hi there,\n\nTruffle does not monitor for changes to your configuration file. It's theoretically possible, but not without excess engineering work for a small benefit. If you change your configuration and would like your contracts recompiled, run `truffle compile --all`. \n\nWe'll reevaluate this if we can come up with a simpler solution with less drawbacks.\n\nCheers!",
